{"tid":805642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"當你覺得拍拖會害到人 請你唔好拍拖","createTime":"2018-09-04T04:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T16:34:01.000Z","uid":133394,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7e31be6b9e78633e6cce0087250c843c8bf57e6d","tid":805642,"uid":133394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"開完呢個post實有朋友會笑鳩我<br />\n但自己真係有感而發<br />\n係中學個陣同d朋友講<br />\n唔想拍拖係怕會傷害到人<br />\n個陣比人笑到臉都黃埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到兩個月前<br />\n我終於拍拖<br />\n然而 自己先發覺自己完全唔享受拍拖<br />\n唔知係雙方不合定係自己貪玩既原因<br />\n無拍拖既時候 講話如果有女朋友會對佢點好點好<br />\n但當我拍拖既時候 我完全提唔起勁起做所有令佢開心既事<br />\n就連應佢都唔係即刻應<br />\n或許我未搵到適合自己既另一半？<br />\n現在已經分手了 希望佢會搵到真正幸福啦<br />\n而我都係做返毒撚算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4ec4a5597c0e324d5986b37f407f7c8ab87792","tid":805642,"uid":194335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:02:10.000Z","msg":"你未脫毒姐"},{"pid":"4c55222bcdf7371f3e98ebc6aeb764861ab4dfb6","tid":805642,"uid":133394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc4ec4a5597c0e324d5986b37f407f7c8ab87792","tid":805642,"uid":194335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:02:10.000Z","msg":"你未脫毒姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"見到d女高質小小就心動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48307a5feffd63c91f2c1a40efb0946020099043","tid":805642,"uid":165202,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"咁係你唔夠中意對方姐"},{"pid":"873eb94914cba892fd3f8af1e40cd87f3c464523","tid":805642,"uid":39055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"根本唔應該開始<br />\n利申 : 情況一樣 但我係被分手既人"},{"pid":"d87ec2b1976bb9dae95e3522501edeeb72ddbb91","tid":805642,"uid":133394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48307a5feffd63c91f2c1a40efb0946020099043","tid":805642,"uid":165202,"like":1,"dislike":2,